title: The One Where They Talk About Names & Stuff
description:
Lala and Randall are podcasting together, and have stories from their location in Puerto Rico, where Lala is shooting a movie!!  They share a baby update, reveal some name stories, and answer a few fan questions, including whether the birth of Baby Girl Emmett will be featured on “Vanderpump Rules” (should the show resume filming soon).

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
